      "text": "A founder of a community transport service that uses the Makkie explains:<blockquote>\nJust going to the local market, to the hospital or to visit someone – those are the type of trips that pose a problem for the elderly. A taxi is too expensive and you have to order a ride with Connexxion (the local public transport company that offers trips for disabled and elderly) way in advance. Just getting dropped off for a small errand at the supermarket is impossible.</blockquote>"
